Requirements
------------

This module requires at least Drupal 4.5.0.

Installation
------------

1. Copy the scheduler.module to the Drupal modules/ directory.
2. Run the scheduler.mysql file to create the necessary database table.
3. Activate the module on the admin/modules page

Notes
-----

Anyone with 'schedule nodes' permission will be able to schedule post and hide
times.  Only those with both the 'schedule nodes' and 'administer nodes'
permissions will be able to administrate schedules.

